female, holotype; 
<emphasis id="355B8A823832159BF687704DEED5BE69" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="45">E, F.</emphasis>
male, paratype) - 
<emphasis id="589B9527F68457443C4122D8432D8378" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="45">A, E.</emphasis>
Habitus; 
<emphasis id="692C3CF89AC7DDC0C90B2D770CDF6F2F" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="45">B, F.</emphasis>
Head, frontal view; 
